Share Data Between Manufacturing Cloud and Data Cloud at Scale Using Data Streams

Connect data on assets, customers, warranties, and sales between Data Cloud and Manufacturing Cloud by using the predefined data streams in the Manufacturing data kit. Seamlessly send the data in Manufacturing Cloud to Data Cloud to query, analyze, and segment the data. Then, use the transformed data to enhance your business processes and give actionable insights to sales and service teams.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions with Manufacturing Cloud and Data Cloud.

How: In Data Cloud, on the Data Streams tab, go to the All list view. Select a data stream, such as AssetMilestone, WorkOrder, or WarrantyTerm.
title: Share Data Between Manufacturing Cloud and Data Cloud
